videos.description: Danny Etling screen pass complete to Leonard Fournette for 38 yds to the Ark 15
videos.headline: Fournette screen pass gets Tigers deep into Arkansas territory

videos.description: LSU takes its opening possession and goes 75 yards in nine plays ending with Leonard Fournette powering his way into the end zone to put the Tigers up 7-0.
videos.headline: One drive, one Fournette TD for LSU

videos.description: Austin Allen pass intercepted by Donnie Alexander and returned 14 yds to the Ark 18
videos.headline: LSU interception sets up the Tigers with great field position

videos.description: After an interception puts LSU in business, Leonard Fournette cashes in from seven yards out for his second touchdown of the game to put the Tigers up 14-0.
videos.headline: Fournette powers to the end zone for second time

videos.description: After getting caught in the backfield, Leonard Fournette limps off the field with a lower leg injury.
videos.headline: Fournette limps off after getting twisted down

videos.description: After Leonard Fournette limped off to the sidelines, Derrius Guice picks up without missing a beat as he punches it in from three yards out to put LSU up 21-0.
videos.headline: Arkansas has no answer as LSU scores on the ground again

videos.description: Devwah Whaley runs for 34 yds and big finish
videos.headline: Arkansas' Devwah Whaley stiff-arms his way to big gain

videos.description: After spotting LSU a 21-0 lead, Arkansas goes for it all when Austin Allen hits Dominique Reed for a 44-yard touchdown to get the Razorbacks to within 14.
videos.headline: Arkansas strikes back with 44-yard TD pass
LSU head coach Ed Orgeron knows his team is in for a 60 minute fight
Arkansas head coach Bret Bielema wants his team to improve on 3rd down conversions in 2nd half

videos.description: For the second time in the last three games, Leonard Fournette finds the end zone three times, the latest from three yards out to put LSU up 28-10.
videos.headline: Another game, another Fournette TD hat trick

videos.description: Tre'Davious White fumbles punt and it is recovered by Arkansas' Cody Hollister
videos.headline: LSU muffed punt keeps Razorbacks' chances alive

videos.description: Austin Allen pass complete to Rawleigh Williams III for 54 yds
videos.headline: R. Williams III with impressive 54 yard gain

videos.description: Leonard Fournette might get the headlines but Derrius Guice is having himself a game, going 96 yards for his second touchdown of the game and giving him over 250 yards on the ground for LSU.
videos.headline: Guice ices the game with 96-yard TD for LSU

videos.description: LSU interim head coach Ed Orgeron expresses his happiness with the Tigers in their victory against Arkansas.
videos.headline: Orgeron: 'Proud of everybody' in win over Hogs
Breakdown of 38-10 LSU victory over Arkansas

videos.description: Leonard Fournette teams up with Derrius Guice to rush for a combined 350 yards and 5 touchdowns in LSU's win over Arkansas.
videos.headline: LSU's RB duo slices through Arkansas
